<DOC><DOCNO> WSJ880315-0126 </DOCNO><HL> McDonnell Unit Gets $24.1 Million Navy Job </HL><SO> </SO><CO> MD ALD GE </CO><G> DEF </G><DATELINE> WASHINGTON  </DATELINE><TEXT>   McDonnell Aircraft Co., a unit of McDonnell Douglas Corp., got a $24.1 million Navy contract for AV-8B aircraft production.    Allied-Signal Inc. was issued a $17 million Navy contract for sonar equipment for SH-60F helicopters.    General Electric Co. won a $10.7 million Navy contract for naval nuclear-propulsion research and development. </TEXT></DOC>